inair.collection

Class CollectionChangedEventArgs

  • java.lang.Object
    • inair.collection.CollectionChangedEventArgs

  • public class CollectionChangedEventArgs
extends java.lang.Object
    Arguments for the CollectionChanged event. A collection that supports NotifyCollectionChanged This raises this event whenever an item is added or removed, or when the contents of the collection changes dramatically.
